\begin_inset Formula $d$
\end_inset

 of them and 
\begin_inset Formula $4dp\leq1$
\end_inset

, then:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
Pr\left[\stackrel[i=1]{n}{\bigcap}\overline{\mathcal{E}}_{i}\right]>0
\]

